{"thag16.3:0.1":"Theragatha 16.3 ","thag16.3:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.3:0.4":"Telakanittheragatha ","thag16.3:1.1":"“Cirarattam vatatapi, ","thag16.3:1.2":"dhammam anuvicintayam; ","thag16.3:1.3":"Samam cittassa nalattham, ","thag16.3:1.4":"puccham samanabrahmane. ","thag16.3:2.1":"‘Ko so parangato loke, ","thag16.3:2.2":"ko patto amatogadham; ","thag16.3:2.3":"Kassa dhammam paticchami, ","thag16.3:2.4":"paramatthavijananam’. ","thag16.3:3.1":"Antovankagato asi, ","thag16.3:3.2":"macchova ghasamamisam; ","thag16.3:3.3":"Baddho mahindapasena, ","thag16.3:3.4":"vepacityasuro yatha. ","thag16.3:4.1":"Anchami nam na muncami, ","thag16.3:4.2":"asma sokapariddava; ","thag16.3:4.3":"Ko me bandham muncam loke, ","thag16.3:4.4":"sambodhim vedayissati. ","thag16.3:5.1":"Samanam brahmanam va kam, ","thag16.3:5.2":"adisantam pabhangunam; ","thag16.3:5.3":"Kassa dhammam paticchami, ","thag16.3:5.4":"jaramaccupavahanam. ","thag16.3:6.1":"Vicikicchakankhaganthitam, ","thag16.3:6.2":"sarambhabalasannutam; ","thag16.3:6.3":"Kodhappattamanatthaddham, ","thag16.3:6.4":"abhijappappadaranam. ","thag16.3:7.1":"Tanhadhanusamutthanam, ","thag16.3:7.2":"dve ca pannarasayutam; ","thag16.3:7.3":"Passa orasikam balham, ","thag16.3:7.4":"bhetvana yadi titthati. ","thag16.3:8.1":"Anuditthinam appahanam, ","thag16.3:8.2":"sankappaparatejitam; ","thag16.3:8.3":"Tena viddho pavedhami, ","thag16.3:8.4":"pattamva maluteritam. ","thag16.3:9.1":"Ajjhattam me samutthaya, ","thag16.3:9.2":"khippam paccati mamakam; ","thag16.3:9.3":"Chaphassayatani kayo, ","thag16.3:9.4":"yattha sarati sabbada. ","thag16.3:10.1":"Tam na passami tekiccham, ","thag16.3:10.2":"yo metam sallamuddhare; ","thag16.3:10.3":"Nanarajjena satthena, ","thag16.3:10.4":"nannena vicikicchitam. ","thag16.3:11.1":"Ko me asattho avano, ","thag16.3:11.2":"Sallamabbhantarapassayam; ","thag16.3:11.3":"Ahimsam sabbagattani, ","thag16.3:11.4":"Sallam me uddharissati. ","thag16.3:12.1":"Dhammappati hi so settho, ","thag16.3:12.2":"visadosappavahako; ","thag16.3:12.3":"Gambhire patitassa me, ","thag16.3:12.4":"thalam paninca dassaye. ","thag16.3:13.1":"Rahadehamasmi ogalho, ","thag16.3:13.2":"ahariyarajamattike; ","thag16.3:13.3":"Mayausuyasarambha, ","thag16.3:13.4":"thinamiddhamapatthate. ","thag16.3:14.1":"Uddhaccameghathanitam, ","thag16.3:14.2":"samyojanavalahakam; ","thag16.3:14.3":"Vaha vahanti kudditthim, ","thag16.3:14.4":"sankappa raganissita. ","thag16.3:15.1":"Savanti sabbadhi sota, ","thag16.3:15.2":"lata ubbhijja titthati; ","thag16.3:15.3":"Te sote ko nivareyya, ","thag16.3:15.4":"tam latam ko hi checchati. ","thag16.3:16.1":"Velam karotha bhaddante, ","thag16.3:16.2":"sotanam sannivaranam; ","thag16.3:16.3":"Ma te manomayo soto, ","thag16.3:16.4":"rukkhamva sahasa luve. ","thag16.3:17.1":"Evam me bhayajatassa, ","thag16.3:17.2":"apara paramesato; ","thag16.3:17.3":"Tano pannavudho sattha, ","thag16.3:17.4":"isisanghanisevito. ","thag16.3:18.1":"Sopanam sugatam suddham, ","thag16.3:18.2":"dhammasaramayam dalham; ","thag16.3:18.3":"Padasi vuyhamanassa, ","thag16.3:18.4":"‘ma bhayi’ti ca mabravi. ","thag16.3:19.1":"Satipatthanapasadam, ","thag16.3:19.2":"aruyha paccavekkhisam; ","thag16.3:19.3":"Yam tam pubbe amannissam, ","thag16.3:19.4":"sakkayabhiratam pajam. ","thag16.3:20.1":"Yada ca maggamaddakkhim, ","thag16.3:20.2":"navaya abhiruhanam; ","thag16.3:20.3":"Anadhitthaya attanam, ","thag16.3:20.4":"titthamaddakkhimuttamam. ","thag16.3:21.1":"Sallam attasamutthanam, ","thag16.3:21.2":"bhavanettippabhavitam; ","thag16.3:21.3":"Etesam appavattaya, ","thag16.3:21.4":"desesi maggamuttamam. ","thag16.3:22.1":"Digharattanusayitam, ","thag16.3:22.2":"cirarattamadhitthitam; ","thag16.3:22.3":"Buddho mepanudi gantham, ","thag16.3:22.4":"visadosappavahano”ti. ","thag16.3:22.5":"… Telakani thero …. "}